                 -- Installation Instructions --

This release of Pines is stable and can be installed in a production
environment.

## Requirements for Pines ##
	* PHP (v5.3 and up)

## Requirements for the Database Backends ##
	* MySQL (v5.0 and up)
	or
	* PostgreSQL (v8.4 and up) (Installing the PL/Perl extension will
	  significantly improve performance in most scenarios.)

## Installation Steps ##
	1. Extract Pines to your server.
	2. Go to its address in a browser.
	3. Follow the steps to setup your database.
	4. Register a new user, by selecting the "I'm new." option. The system will
	   detect that there are no other users and grant the new user all
	   abilities.

Good luck. ;)